npm init -y

Inside package.json, add:
"type": "module",
It'll allow import and export keyword.

npm i express nodemon
nodemon is used for re-starting server automatically.

Inside "scripts" of package.json, add:
"start": "node index.js",
"dev": "nodemon index.js"

node -v

npm i mongoose

npm i cors

Frontend:
npm i axios 
npm i react-icons